author: news.yahoo.com
title: Paisley, Church, Hunt to headline 2016 Big Barrel festival
text:
DOVER, Del. (AP) — Brad Paisley, Eric Church and Sam Hunt will headline the Big Barrel Country Music Festival next year.
Festival organizer announced their 2016 lineup Monday. The three-day festival kicks off June 24 at The Woodlands near Dover International Speedway.
The festival will also feature Hank Williams Jr., Emmylou Harris, Jason Isbell, Robert Earl Keen, Pokey LaFarge, Dwight Yoakam, Marty Stuart and Travis Tritt. Other acts include Tyler Farr, Eli Young Band, Martina McBride, The Band Perry and Lee Brice.
Tickets for the three-day festival and camping packages go on sale Friday.
